283
00:16:31.721 --> 00:16:32.921
A thinner?

284
00:16:32.921 --> 00:16:34.121
Yes.

285
00:16:34.121 --> 00:16:37.721
In volatile solvents such as turpentine and petrol,

286
00:16:37.721 --> 00:16:40.521
