380
00:23:24.421 --> 00:23:28.121
Your ear, your ear.

381
00:23:28.121 --> 00:23:32.321
Oh, my God. Why is this on my ear?

382
00:23:32.321 --> 00:23:35.021
It's strange. Mysterious things do happen.

383
00:23:35.021 --> 00:23:37.021
What a poor sport!

